# Ollama Cloud API key.
# Set this when using Ollama Cloud (https://ollama.com/cloud) as the backend for
# ollama_local adapter agents.  Agents can override this via the "apiKey" field
# in their adapterConfig; this env var acts as a server-wide fallback.
# OLLAMA_API_KEY=
